p: Among the pregnant women surveyed, 906 (26.3%) had been exposed to ZIKV. Most pregnant women were precarious 2475/3439. The proportion of precarious women was significantly greater in ZIKV confirmed 728/906 (80.4%) than the ZIKV negatives 1747/2533 (69.0%), p<0.0001. Among precarious, irregular immigrants seemed more exposed 97/300 (32.3%) than French nationals 361/ 1310 (27.6%) (p = 0.10).
